Package Applicant

Class Applicant

java.lang.Object
Users.User
Applicant.Applicant
Direct Known Subclasses:
HdbOfficer
public class Applicant extends User
Represents an applicant for residential applications, including personal details and associated enquiries. Inherits from the User class and adds functionality for residential application and enquiry management.
